title: Chris Wraight - Warhammer 40k - Scars
description: Of all the Legiones Astartes, the White Scars of Jaghatai Khan remain the most enigmatic and elusive. But when the Alpha Legion launch an unexplained and simultaneous attack against the White Scars and Space Wolves, the Khan must decide once and for all whether he will stand with the Emperor or the Warmaster... or neither.
